HEADWORD: Phytography
<hw>Phy*tog"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Phyto-</ets> + <ets>-graphy</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>phytographie</ets>.]</ety> <def>The science of describing plants in
